{"tha-ap319:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap319:0.2":"Arakkhadayakavagga ","tha-ap319:0.3":"Saddasannakattheraapadana ","tha-ap319:1.1":"“Sudassano mahaviro, ","tha-ap319:1.2":"deseti amatam padam; ","tha-ap319:1.3":"Parivuto savakehi, ","tha-ap319:1.4":"vasati gharamuttame. ","tha-ap319:2.1":"Taya vacaya madhuraya, ","tha-ap319:2.2":"sanganhati mahajanam; ","tha-ap319:2.3":"Ghoso ca vipulo asi, ","tha-ap319:2.4":"asiso devamanuse. ","tha-ap319:3.1":"Nigghosasaddam sutvana, ","tha-ap319:3.2":"siddhatthassa mahesino; ","tha-ap319:3.3":"Sadde cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap319:3.4":"avandim lokanayakam. ","tha-ap319:4.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap319:4.2":"yam sannamalabhim tada; ","tha-ap319:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap319:4.4":"buddhasannayidam phalam. ","tha-ap319:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap319:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap319:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap319:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma saddasannako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap319:7.1":"Saddasannakattherassapadanam sattamam. "}